Šimon Ornest: We want to gather positive energy at concerts
What do you think about the end of the world in less than a month?
It's just one of the other alarm messages that we humans like to catch on to us.
Together with The Tap Tap, we make fun of it and we say that we are the only band in the world that can gather enough positive energy to delay or prevent the end of the world.
In December, you will organize a completely unique project of three concerts against the end of the world.
Can you introduce it to readers in more detail?
It is a nationwide benefit event that we have been planning for two years.
We decided to use the marketing potential of the end of the Mayan calendar announced on December 21 at 11:10 a.m.
The day before 20 December at 21 o'CL o'CLight, 3 concerts will be held in Prague, Brno and Ostrava.
